The array `nums` should have a 0-indexed format.The input array `nums` should have a length of `n`.The length of the output array `ans` should be equal to the length of the input array `nums`.The score of the prefix `nums[0 .  . i]` should be assigned to the value of `ans[i]` in the method, where the parameter array `nums` is sorted in ascending order.The sum of all the elements in the prefix `nums[0 .  . i]` is the score of the prefix, where `nums` is an array of integers.